---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Music
description: "Listen to DJ Sprenk's Brazilian Zouk mixes on Mixcloud and SoundCloud — new sets posted weekly. Over 3 million minutes streamed and 100,000+ listens."
---

<h1>Music</h1>

<p>
  Listen on
  <a href="{{ site.social.mixcloud }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mixcloud</a> or
  <a href="{{ site.social.soundcloud }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SoundCloud</a>. New posts weekly on Wednesdays!
</p>

<p></p>

<h2>Start Here</h2>

<p>New to DJ Sprenk? start here!</p>

<div class="featured-sets">
  {% for set in featured_sets %}
  <div class="featured-set">
    <iframe
      class="mixcloud-embed"
      title="{{ set.title }} – Mixcloud player"
      src="https://www.mixcloud.com/widget/iframe/?feed=/djsprenk/{{ set.slug }}/&hide_cover=1&mini=1&autoplay=0"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="autoplay"
      loading="lazy"
    ></iframe>
    {% if set.note %}
    <p class="featured-set-note">{{ set.note }}</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
